{"title":"SAA \/ Sex \u0026 Love","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: #0000ff;\"\u003eAny questions, please call us (212) 794-3858\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAs a fellowship of recovering addicts, Sex Addicts Anonymous offers a message of hope to anyone who suffers from sex addiction.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","products":[{"product_id":"hope-and-recovery-a-twelve-step-guide-for-healing-from-compulsive-sexual-behavior","title":"Hope and Recovery: A Twelve Step Guide for Healing from Compulsive Sexual Behavior","description":"\u003cp\u003eA remarkable work, \u003cem\u003eHope and Recovery\u003c\/em\u003e guides and supports the life-transforming move from self-defeating and destructive sexual behavior to healthy, affirming sexuality. This widely acclaimed contribution to addiction literature applies the Twelve Step Program of Alcoholics Anonymous to the complex problem of sex addiction.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hazelden","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":1024228695,"sku":null,"price":18.95,"currency_code":"USD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0685\/9435\/products\/hope-and-recovery-a-twelve-step-guide-for-healing-from-compulsive-sexual-behavior.jpeg?v=1585854851"},{"product_id":"out-of-the-shadows-understanding-sexual-addiction-softcover","title":"Out of the Shadows Understanding Sexual Addiction Softcover","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eOut of the Shadows\u003c\/em\u003e, the first work ever published on sexual addiction, remains the premier text in the field. It is a compelling, breakthrough work offering hope for those who had no hope and insight for those who want to learn how and why this addiction occurs. Dr. Carnes examines the tangled web of love, addictive sex, hate and fear that is usually founded in family relationships. He details what happens and what to expect when sexual addiction is present. And he offers a way for addicts and codependents to deal with their sexual compulsions, as well as their whole life, to become more whole human beings.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hazelden","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":1024230895,"sku":null,"price":16.95,"currency_code":"USD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0685\/9435\/products\/out-of-the-shadows-understanding-sexual-addiction-softcover.jpeg?v=1585854603"},{"product_id":"sex-love-addicts-anonymous-basic-text","title":"Sex \u0026 Love Addicts Anonymous Basic Text, Softcover","description":"\u003cp\u003eThe Basic Text for the Augustine Fellowship, Sex and Love Addicts Anonymous \u003cbr\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAuthor:\u003c\/strong\u003e SLAA\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSoftcover, 280 pages\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe basic text describing how this Twelve Step fellowship interprets AA's program to give support to recovering sex addicts. Includes many personal stories.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Augustine Fellowship","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":1024231735,"sku":null,"price":24.95,"currency_code":"USD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0685\/9435\/products\/sex-love-addicts-anonymous-basic-text-softcover.jpeg?v=1585854646"},{"product_id":"sexaholics-anonymous-basic-text","title":"Sexaholics Anonymous Basic Text","description":"\u003cp\u003eThe basic text for Sexaholics Anonymous. This book is for those who want to stop their sexually self-destructive thinking and behavior. It was written piece by piece as the need arose during the emergence and growth of SA. In this book we describe how these principles are working for us. When based on a foundation of sexual sobriety and put into personal action, the Twelve Steps and Twelve Traditions become the beginning of a whole new way of life.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"SA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":1024231739,"sku":null,"price":16.95,"currency_code":"USD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0685\/9435\/products\/sexaholics-anonymous-basic-text.jpeg?v=1585854648"},{"product_id":"sexual-anorexia-overcoming-sexual-self-hatred","title":"Sexual Anorexia: Overcoming Sexual Self-Hatred","description":"\u003cp\u003eA first-time examination of sexual anorexia, an extreme fear of sexual intimacy and obsessive avoidance of sex, by the acknowledged leader in the treatment of compulsive sexual behavior and recovery.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eAuthor Dr. Patrick Carnes begins by defining sexual anorexia and demonstrating how it and it's parallel disorder, sexual addiction and compulsivity, often arise from a background of childhood sexual trauma, neglect, and other forms of abuse, Carnes explores the numerous dimensions of sexual health, examining key issues which must be addressed and resolved for recovery to proceed. Utilizing extensive research and elucidating case studies, Carnes develops concrete tasks and plans for restoring nurturing and sensuality, building fulfilling relationships, exploring intimacy, and creating healthy sexuality. Woven throughout the book are stories of recovery which illustrate sexual healing principles, model new behavior, and support motivation for change.Sexual Anorexia enables those suffering from this disorder to recognize that sex need not be a furtive enemy to be fought and defeated but, instead, a deeply sensual, passionate, fulfilling, and spiritual experience that all human beings are innately entitled to.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003ePatrick Carnes, Ph.D., the best-selling author of Out of the Shadows and Contrary to Love, is an internationally known speaker and writer on sexual dysfunction and recovery. He is currently Clinical Director of Sexual Disorders at The Meadows, a treatment facility that works with clients who deal with a wide range of behavior disorders, addiction, and psychological conditions.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hazelden","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":1024231747,"sku":null,"price":16.95,"currency_code":"USD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0685\/9435\/products\/sexual-anorexia-overcoming-sexual-self-hatred.jpeg?v=1585854648"},{"product_id":"facing-love-addiction-giving-yourself-the-power-to-change-the-way-you-love-by-pia-mellody","title":"Facing Love Addiction: Giving Yourself the Power to Change the Way You Love, by Pia Mellody","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis groundbreaking exploration from the author of the best-selling \"Facing Codependence and Breaking Free\" unravels the intricate and debilitating dynamics of co-addicted relationships.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eMellody clearly outlines the \"toxic\" patterns played out by Love Addicts and the unresponsive Avoidance Addicts to whom they are painfully and repeatedly drawn. She shares personal experience and real case histories that clarify the distinctions between codependence (how our relationship with our self fails) and co-addiction (how our relations with others become unhealthy entanglements) describe how \"love at first sight\" can be the first step in the addictive cycle of attraction, fantasy, denial, and obsession show how childhood experiences of abandonment or engulfment influence our choice of romantic partners, friends, and associates detail the tango-like way that addicts activate one another's primary fears and literally \"bring out the worst in each other.\"\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"None","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":1024227759,"sku":null,"price":16.95,"currency_code":"USD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0685\/9435\/products\/facing-love-addiction-giving-yourself-the-power-to-change-the-way-you-love-by-pia-mellody.jpg?v=1585854826"},{"product_id":"sex-addicts-anonymous-basic-text-soft-cover-pocket-edition","title":"Sex Addicts Anonymous Basic Text - Soft Cover Pocket Edition","description"